headline: A Look Back at Water Infrastructure Stocks’ Q4 Earnings: Tennant (NYSE:TNC) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Tennant (NYSE:TNC) and the rest of the water infrastructure stocks fared in Q4.
